## 2. Servicios de Datos (Data Services)

### 2.1 Feature Service

**URL Pattern**: `{serviceUrl}/FeatureServer`

#### Operaciones del Service:
```
GET .../FeatureServer                    # Info del servicio
GET .../FeatureServer/{layerId}          # Info de capa
GET .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/query    # Consultar features
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/addFeatures
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/updateFeatures
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/deleteFeatures
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/applyEdits  # Operación combinada
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/addAttachment
GET .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/queryAttachments
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/calculateField
POST .../FeatureServer/{layerId}/generateRenderer
```

#### Query Parameters:
| Parámetro | Tipo | Ejemplo |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `where` | string | `"POPULATION > 50000"` |
| `outFields` | string | `"NAME,POPULATION,AREA"` o `"*"` |
| `geometry` | JSON | `{"xmin":...,"ymin":...,"xmax":...,"ymax":...}` |
| `geometryType` | string | esriGeometryPoint, esriGeometryEnvelope, esriGeometryPolygon |
| `spatialRel` | string | esriSpatialRelIntersects, esriSpatialRelContains, esriSpatialRelWithin |
| `returnGeometry` | bool | true/false |
| `resultRecordCount` | int | Límite de registros (paginación) |
| `resultOffset` | int | Offset para paginación |
| `orderByFields` | string | `"POPULATION DESC"` |
| `groupByFieldsForStatistics` | string | Campos para agrupar |
| `outStatistics` | JSON | `[{"statisticType":"sum","onStatisticField":"POP","outStatisticFieldName":"TotalPop"}]` |
| `returnDistinctValues` | bool | Valores únicos |
| `returnCountOnly` | bool | Solo retornar conteo |
| `distance` | double | Distancia de buffer |
| `units` | string | esriSRUnit_Meter, esriSRUnit_Kilometer |

### 2.2 Vector Tile Service
```
GET {serviceUrl}/VectorTileServer
GET {serviceUrl}/VectorTileServer/resources/styles/root.json  # Style spec (Mapbox)
GET {serviceUrl}/VectorTileServer/tile/{z}/{y}/{x}.pbf        # Tiles protobuf
```

### 2.3 Map Tile Service (Raster)
```
GET {serviceUrl}/MapServer/tile/{z}/{y}/{x}  # Tiles PNG/JPEG
GET {serviceUrl}/MapServer/export             # Dynamic image export
```

### 2.4 Image Service
```
GET {serviceUrl}/ImageServer
GET {serviceUrl}/ImageServer/query
GET {serviceUrl}/ImageServer/exportImage
GET {serviceUrl}/ImageServer/identify
POST {serviceUrl}/ImageServer/computeHistograms
POST {serviceUrl}/ImageServer/computeStatisticsHistograms
```

