## 3. Portal REST API

### 3.1 Content Management
```
# Buscar items
GET /sharing/rest/search?q=title:"my map" AND type:"Web Map"&num=10&f=json

# CRUD de items
GET /sharing/rest/content/items/{itemId}
GET /sharing/rest/content/items/{itemId}/data
POST /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/addItem
POST /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/items/{itemId}/update
POST /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/items/{itemId}/delete
POST /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/items/{itemId}/share

# Gestión de folders
POST /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/createFolder
GET /sharing/rest/content/users/{username}/{folderId}
```

### 3.2 User Management
```
GET /sharing/rest/community/self         # Usuario actual
GET /sharing/rest/community/users/{username}
POST /sharing/rest/portals/self/createUser
POST /sharing/rest/community/users/{username}/update
GET /sharing/rest/community/users?q=...
```

### 3.3 Group Management
```
GET /sharing/rest/community/groups/{groupId}
POST /sharing/rest/community/createGroup
POST /sharing/rest/community/groups/{groupId}/update
GET /sharing/rest/content/groups/{groupId}
POST /sharing/rest/community/groups/{groupId}/invite
```

### 3.4 Organization/Portal
```
GET /sharing/rest/portals/self           # Info del portal
POST /sharing/rest/portals/self/update   # Actualizar configuración
GET /sharing/rest/portals/self/users     # Usuarios de la org
```

---

## 4. Geoprocessing Services

### Ejecución Sincrónica
```
POST {serviceUrl}/GPServer/{taskName}/execute
Params: Parámetros de entrada específicos de la tarea
Response: { results: [{paramName, dataType, value}] }
```

### Ejecución Asincrónica
```
# 1. Submit job
POST {serviceUrl}/GPServer/{taskName}/submitJob
Response: { jobId, jobStatus: "esriJobSubmitted" }

# 2. Check status
GET {serviceUrl}/GPServer/{taskName}/jobs/{jobId}
Response: { jobStatus: "esriJobSucceeded" | "esriJobFailed" | "esriJobExecuting" }

# 3. Get results
GET {serviceUrl}/GPServer/{taskName}/jobs/{jobId}/results/{outputParamName}
```

### Tipos de datos GP:
- GPFeatureRecordSetLayer, GPRecordSet, GPString, GPDouble, GPLong
- GPBoolean, GPDate, GPLinearUnit, GPDataFile, GPRasterDataLayer

---

## 5. Geometry Service

**URL**: `{serverUrl}/Utilities/Geometry/GeometryServer`

### Operaciones:
```
POST .../project          # Reproyectar geometrías
POST .../buffer           # Crear buffers
POST .../intersect        # Intersección
POST .../union            # Unión
POST .../difference       # Diferencia
POST .../cut              # Cortar
POST .../simplify         # Simplificar
POST .../convexHull       # Envolvente convexa
POST .../areas            # Calcular áreas
POST .../lengths          # Calcular longitudes
POST .../distance         # Calcular distancia
POST .../relation         # Evaluar relaciones espaciales
POST .../densify          # Densificar
POST .../generalize       # Generalizar
POST .../labelPoints      # Puntos de etiqueta
POST .../reshape          # Remodelar
POST .../trimExtend       # Recortar/Extender
POST .../offset           # Desplazar
POST .../autoComplete     # Autocompletar polígonos
```

---

## 6. Notas Importantes

### Límites de Request:
- **GET URLs**: Límite de 1,024 caracteres en algunos servidores → usar POST para payloads grandes
- **Batch Geocoding**: Máximo 1,000 direcciones por lote
- **Feature Query**: Usar paginación con `resultRecordCount` y `resultOffset`
- **Export Map**: Tamaño máximo de imagen depende de la configuración del servidor

### Formato de Geometrías:
```json
// Punto
{"x": -117.19, "y": 34.05, "spatialReference": {"wkid": 4326}}

// Polilínea
{"paths": [[[-117.19, 34.05], [-117.20, 34.06]]], "spatialReference": {"wkid": 4326}}

// Polígono
{"rings": [[[-117.19, 34.05], [-117.20, 34.06], [-117.18, 34.06], [-117.19, 34.05]]], "spatialReference": {"wkid": 4326}}

// Envelope
{"xmin": -117.20, "ymin": 34.04, "xmax": -117.18, "ymax": 34.06, "spatialReference": {"wkid": 4326}}

// Multipoint
{"points": [[-117.19, 34.05], [-117.20, 34.06]], "spatialReference": {"wkid": 4326}}
```

### Spatial References comunes:
| WKID | Nombre | Uso |
|------|--------|-----|
| 4326 | WGS 84 (Geographic) | GPS, datos globales |
| 3857 | Web Mercator | Web maps, tiles |
| 102100 | Web Mercator Auxiliary Sphere | Alias de 3857 en ArcGIS |

### Tokens en requests:
```
# Como query parameter
GET {serviceUrl}/query?where=1=1&f=json&token={access_token}

# Como header HTTP
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
```
